Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.85,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I want to go
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:29.98,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}住み慣れたこの街を出てゆくの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.15,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}新しい世界を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}まだ見ぬ色を　探しに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:38.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I can not do
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:44.49,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}素直になれないこともあるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.49,0:21:47.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}あの虹の向こうへ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:50.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}行ってみたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:58.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}頭に浮かんだイメージを抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:04.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I will never ever give up halfway
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:12.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}どこまでも　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:19.53,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}I wanna make my life shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.53,0:22:30.45,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}輝くよ　あの虹の向こうまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.85,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想要出发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:29.98,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}离开这熟悉的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.15,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}去探索新世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:37.07,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}寻找从未见过的色彩
